{"tid":2253102,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"衛詩雅用冲涼毛巾扮禰豆子 向關智斌陳家樂挑機","createTime":"2020-10-22T02:47:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T03:56:05.000Z","uid":25345,"like":4,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9d855123dee0e3b9fa818f4ce7c1c68fea60902c","tid":2253102,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T02:47:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20201021/s00009/f4468ffb0573462da9daf8d88d736c42.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20201021%2Fs00009%2Ff4468ffb0573462da9daf8d88d736c42.jpg&h=180ce359&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n衛詩雅這個山寨版「禰豆子」也算交足功課。<br />\n<br />\n日本人氣漫畫《鬼滅之刃》大受歡迎，繼關智斌Cosplay扮劇中角色「伊之助」後，衛詩雅今晚亦在網上分享她扮「禰豆子」的照片，還向關智斌及陳家樂來個「鬼滅之刃Cosplay Challenge」，看來她不知道關智斌已快她一步玩過了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\npowered by Rubicon Project<br />\n衛詩雅留言：「彌（禰）荳（豆）子家居山寨low cost cosplay，我盡咗力啦😌 #枉阿妹粉紅絲帶頭夾🎀 #有味沖涼毛巾變和服👘 #九龍城街市茅根竹蔗條竹蔗🎋 #再加友誼牌key雪景 #山寨版彌（禰）荳（豆）子完成✅ #鬼滅の刃 #彌（禰）豆子 #鬼滅之刃CosplayChallenge @kennyjr @carlosbb」"},{"pid":"e89c6a1e373971cf90553a8008225378e449cd33","tid":2253102,"uid":282625,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T02:48:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f193461c6525ed8cb3885d826df7318b30579606","tid":2253102,"uid":46910,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T02:49:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5692d17a1a504977197fa4a80d106c637ffb7756","tid":2253102,"uid":886,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T02:49:44.000Z","msg":"勁撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://twg